Developer Terms of Use
des: Po, the Dragon Warrior, and Master Shifu need YOU to help defeat some of the most dreaded villains in China. But first, you will need to train with the Dragon Warrior himself. Learn the six styles of kung fu—Mantis, Monkey, Viper, Crane, Tiger, and even the rarest of them all: Panda. Your kung fu fighting skills will determine whether China will be saved.
